  "body": "I use the annotation \"helm.sh/resource-policy\": keep to protect some PVCs from deletion on helm uninstall, which works fine. Alas, on helm upgrade, the PVCs are deleted, taking my data with them.\r\nObserved on Helm 3.0.3 and Helm 3.1.1.\r\n\r\nThis seems to be a regression, as I found this issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/helm/helm/issues/3673\r\n\r\n",
